 --------Singleton Design Pattern -------

 Design Pattern - Since a lot of problems in software development repeats itself, so if problems can repeat, solutions can also repeat.

 Design Pattern helps you to solve most of the commonly occured software deisgn problems.

 Mainly of three types.
 1. Creational : Deals with object creation and how many object can be created.
        a) Singleton : Only one object can be created.
        b) Builder   : Object creation for multiple users, restricting object creation to validated users onyl...
        c) Factory   :
                    i  . Simple
                    ii . Abstract
                    iii. Practical
        d) Prototype and Registry


 2. Behavioural
 3. Structural